                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9679" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OM-0373</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">966 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从“邻避”到“网红”：圣元环保花园工厂的惊天巨变之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From &quot;Dodged&quot; to &quot;Influencer&quot;: The Amazing Road to Change of ShengYuan&#39;s Garden Factory</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">周飞，许松玲，张静雯，盛敬涵，郑舒婷，高嘉辉，林晓涵</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华侨大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">圣元环保股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业运营管理；社区共建；工厂管理；绿色创新；全面质量管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Operation Management; Community Co-Construction; Factory Management;  Green Innovation ; Total Quality Management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“爸爸快看，下面的花园好漂亮呀！”周末午后，家住附近的市民王先生带着妻子和女儿，来到位于城市高处的“云端咖啡厅”享受惬意时光。这座咖啡厅坐落于距离地面近 100 米的高空，来来往往的市民们脸上洋溢着轻松愉悦的笑容，在这里谈天说地，享受着片刻的宁静与美好。王先生一家三口坐在由废弃烟囱精心改造而成的咖啡厅内，透过巨大的落地窗，脚下那片绿意盎然、繁花似锦的圣元垃圾焚烧发电厂尽收眼底。王先生不禁发出一声由衷的感叹：“想当年，这里还是臭气熏天、人人避之不及的垃圾填埋场，谁能想到短短几年时间，就变成了如今这般宛如世外桃源的‘花园工厂’，成了咱们周边居民休闲放松的好去处。”
这座被市民称为 “花园工厂” ，隶属于圣元环保公司，是其城市垃圾处理工厂项目。该项目自启动以来，便致力于打造 “环保示范 + 科普教育”的展示窗口，凭借其卓越的环保成效和创新的展示模式，成功获评国家生态环境部 “环保设施向公众开放优秀案例”。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case describes howShengYuan garden factory has developed from its initial involvement in the waste incineration industry to a garden factory that is an &quot;excellent case of environmental protection facilities open to the public&quot; by the Ministry of Ecology and Environment of the People&#39;s Republic of China.In the process of transformation and upgrading, ShengYuan focus on policy guidance, closely follow the market competition, pioneering, and take the initiative to seek change, and always adhere to the &quot;people-oriented&quot; development concept.ShengYuan continue to optimize the four aspects of production plan and process, equipment maintenance, staff management and quality management, to establish core competitiveness and establish the industry benchmark position.Nowadays, ShengYuan will continue to aim for high-quality development, improve production technology and digitalization, further optimize the management mode, and strive to build an industry-leading environmental protection enterprise that combines leading technology, diversified revenue, advanced management, technological empowerment, and a garden factory.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《运营管理》、《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">约束理论；全面质量管理；可持续运营管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-06</td>
                            </tr>
